  m_text: As a newcomer I must admit that I was at first put off by the length of
    the video, and wondered why she wouldn't just cut it into parts and upload them
    individually. But when I did start watching, I got completely hooked. I don't
    know what kind of wizardry this is but the content just flows so incredibly smoothly
    and naturally that cutting the video into parts would ruin it.
